com.omerozer.knit.schedulers

Class KnitTaskFlow

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.omerozer.knit.schedulers.KnitTaskFlow

  • public class KnitTaskFlow
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is only used by InternalModels generated by KnitProcessor. It provides a stubbing pattern for handling SchedulerInterface tasks.
